{"id":55461,"type":2,"name":"がきデカ","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/a9/aa/55461_nxnxc.jpg","summary":"『がきデカ』は、山上たつひこによる日本の漫画作品。主人公である日本初の少年警察官と自称するこまわり君と、彼が通う「逆向（さかむけ）小学校」の同級生やその周辺のキャラクター達で展開されるギャグ漫画作品。『週刊少年チャンピオン』（秋田書店）にて、1974年44号から1980年52号まで連載され、単行本の発行部数は3000万部を超える。\r\n\r\n1989年にTVアニメ化,ほぼ同時にOVAも作られているが双方で制作会社が全く異なり、声の出演も違う。時期や態勢の異なる再アニメ化は珍しくないが、同時に異なる会社でアニメ化されたケースは当時大変珍しかった。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>搞怪刑事</li><li><span>话数: </span>22</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>1989-10-16</li><li><span>分镜: </span><a href=\"/person/1567\">湖川友謙</a>、<a href=\"/person/1345\">辻初樹</a>、<a href=\"/person/2301\">森本晃司</a></li><li><span>演出: </span><a href=\"/person/2301\">森本晃司</a>、<a href=\"/person/1345\">辻初樹</a>、<a href=\"/person/1567\">湖川友謙</a></li><li><span>美术监督: </span><a href=\"/person/6333\">小林七郎</a></li><li><span>总作画监督: </span><a href=\"/person/1345\">辻初樹</a></li><li><span>作画监督: </span><a href=\"/person/1567\">湖川友謙</a>、<a href=\"/person/1345\">辻初樹</a></li><li><span>原画: </span><a href=\"/person/2653\">金田伊功</a></li><li><span>播放结束: </span>1990-03-26</li>","collection":{"wish":4,"collect":2,"on_hold":2,"dropped":3},"tags":[{"name":"1989","count":3},{"name":"TV","count":2},{"name":"StudioGallop","count":1},{"name":"山田雄三","count":1},{"name":"三ツ矢雄二","count":1},{"name":"古谷徹","count":1},{"name":"TVA","count":1},{"name":"日本动画","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":214938,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/214938","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":214939,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/214939","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":214940,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/214940","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":214941,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/214941","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":214942,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/214942","type":